Release: 1%{?dist}
Summary: Replace Object.assign with an inline helper
License: MIT
URL: http://babeljs.io/
Source0: http://registry.npmjs.org/babel-plugin-transform-object-assign/-/babel-plugin-transform-object-assign-6.8.0.tgz
